<h1 style="font-family:verdana">TradeTracker DevOPS Assesment</h1>
<hr>
<p><b style="font-family:verdana">Following are the tasks which we are doing here in this Assesment: </p></b>
<pre><p>
    <b>a. /setup
    Purpose:</b> Prepare nodes for load balancer upon receiving GitHub push event.

    <b>b. /test
    Purpose:</b> Testing end point where you are required to generate random record with 3 attributes 
    (first name, last name, age) and insert it into a PostgreSQL DB.

    <b>c. /takedown
    Purpose:</b> Remove a node from the PostgreSQL cluster.

    <b>d. /transfer
    Purpose:</b> Move data currently stored in PostgreSQL in NoSQL engine.

    <b>e. /count
    Purpose:</b> Return the count of records stored in NoSQL engine.

    <b>f. /teardown
    Purpose:</b> Dispose-off resources.

</pre></p>
